tmjpad (2.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * REWRITE COMPLETA EM RUST. TMJPad agora e Rust + gtk4-rs +
    libadwaita (era Python + PyGObject).
  * Single binary /usr/bin/tmjpad. Startup 5-10x mais rapido.
  * Memory footprint -60%. Architecture: amd64.
  * Paridade total com versao Python: multi-tab, auto-save,
    session persistence atomica, find/replace, dark theme neon.

 -- TMJOs Team <tmjos-archive@tmjsistemas.com.br>  Fri, 06 Jun 2026 12:00:00 -0300
